ability0.name: Ability 1
ability0.text: {fontsize-20}{color#ffffff}Whenever a creature card is put into an opponent’s graveyard from anywhere, put a loyalty counter on {Cardname}{/color#ffffff}

ability1.name: Ability 2
ability1.text: {fontsize-20}{color#ffffff}Each opponent discards a card, mills two cards, and loses 2 life. You draw a card.

ability3.name: Ability 4
ability3.text: {color#ffffff}{fontsize-20}Each opponent exiles the top five cards of their library face down. You may look at and play those cards without paying their mana costs for as long as they remain exiled.
